Dependencies:
- Qt4 libraries and devel packages (QtCore, QtGui, QtSql)
- Kde4 library and devel package

Installation instructions:
>$ git clone https://github.com/riccardobellini/VehicleReminder.git
>$ cd VehicleReminder
>$ mkdir build && cd build
>$ cmake ..
>$ make
>$ make install (may require execution as root)